Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.82,0:02:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼重新打個招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.61,0:02:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好嗎 Cygnus的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.82,0:02:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒變呢 費爾米博士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.87,0:02:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長 前方有艦艇接近
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.41,0:03:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是聯結系統實驗艦Crane
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.54,0:03:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(656,488)}聯結實驗艦Crane
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到Cygnus
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.51,0:03:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常歡迎您
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 美麗的小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.93,0:03:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看您這麼精神我太開心了 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.52,0:03:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.06,0:03:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你臉上又添小皺紋啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.90,0:03:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師你又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.24,0:03:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 恕我唐突
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.49,0:03:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯結系統的公開表演？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.28,0:03:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.24,0:03:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你們能展示給費爾米博士看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.41,0:03:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託咯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.79,0:03:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他似乎是為了這個才特地從夏威夷趕來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.83,0:03:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從夏威夷來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.25,0:03:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我們很快就要抵達的夏威夷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.59,0:03:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是不願再等下去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.63,0:03:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 LUXON現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好座艙區域沒有損壞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.55,0:03:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是可能聯結的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個老爺子就是聯結系統的開發者呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準確來說應該是開發小組的領隊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.73,0:04:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提出聯結理論的確實是費爾米博士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.61,0:04:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是以博士的研究室為主體 開發了系統
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.62,0:04:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但之所以能夠實用化
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.62,0:04:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要歸功於所員艾維拉小姐開發的座艙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 我是好處都被徒弟拿走的糊塗師傅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.92,0:04:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博…博士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是糊塗師傅不也挺好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在艾維拉君的爺爺那裡開始聯結的基礎研究的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.81,0:04:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 從她還裹著尿布的時候就認識她了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.69,0:04:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.65,0:04:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她裹尿布一直裹到很大年紀 大家都很擔心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.19,0:04:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.57,0:05:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 那個小姑娘現在卻是遠在我之上的研究者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.78,0:05:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能不高興吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.16,0:05:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有段佳話呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.12,0:05:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閒談就到此為止吧 開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.33,0:05:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡瀨少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.92,0:05:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連接迪奧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.38,0:05:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.80,0:05:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,emphatier振動數安定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,enharmonic控制竟然能完成到如此地步
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.43,0:05:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.52,0:05:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯結的持續時間是多少
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.56,0:05:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實用界限值300秒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.66,0:05:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距解除聯結還有10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.12,0:05:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.08,0:05:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.12,0:05:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.12,0:05:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.46,0:05:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除聯結
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.38,0:06:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系統和駕駛員都沒有異常
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了 青葉君 迪奧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.18,0:06:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.61,0:06:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你騙得了機器 別以為就能騙過我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.69,0:06:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼騙不騙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.66,0:06:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你見到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.07,0:06:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那座島上見到了那個叫雛的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.16,0:06:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.33,0:06:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要編那種一戳就破的謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.29,0:06:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的 她不是我認識的雛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.79,0:06:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.29,0:06:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡 在70年後的這個世界裡 沒有雛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.59,0:06:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救了我 把我送到未來的弓原雛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.43,0:06:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.76,0:06:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.93,0:06:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才失落的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.77,0:06:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有失落
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.18,0:06:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你意外還挺纖細的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.10,0:06:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說我沒失落了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.48,0:06:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說 敵方駕駛員知道回過去的方法這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.82,0:07:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是從哪裡聽說的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.61,0:07:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是小學生都能編個更好的故事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.20,0:07:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是編故事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想只有這個方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.37,0:07:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.75,0:07:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.21,0:07:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒了沒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.80,0:07:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還想哭喪著臉到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.17,0:07:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LUXON已經修理完了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你這樣的傢伙還是不在…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.93,0:07:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭喪著臉的 是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前不久還在為妹妹煩惱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少在那裡自以為是的教訓別人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.19,0:07:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.07,0:07:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟菲奧娜沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.95,0:07:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個妹控
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴 你這個不乾脆的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.50,0:07:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆在幹嗎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.96,0:07:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別打啦 迪奧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.59,0:08:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我 你這傢伙 放開我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.59,0:08:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要讓這傢伙清醒過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.64,0:08:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 真能給人添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆有點做過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.47,0:08:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長說讓你們暫時在這裡冷靜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.73,0:08:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓我做多餘的運動啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.16,0:08:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年輕真好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.70,0:08:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 費爾米博士呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.83,0:08:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.04,0:08:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 在了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.63,0:08:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你是從過去來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.63,0:08:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是70年前？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.51,0:08:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你不相信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.84,0:08:53.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於聯結系統你瞭解多少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.31,0:08:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊 簡單來說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.52,0:08:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是將兩個駕駛員的大腦並聯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.65,0:09:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛越提高演算能力的裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個系統的關鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.53,0:09:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在於令兩人的思考毫無延遲地傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.12,0:09:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為時滯會影響戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.41,0:09:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思考毫無延遲？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.66,0:09:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼對那個笨蛋說明都是白費力氣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.75,0:09:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.29,0:09:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 因為現在僅僅隔著一面牆壁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.26,0:09:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以這樣交流
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.34,0:09:30.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在戰場上可不能這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.89,0:09:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離越遠延遲越大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.89,0:09:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是納秒等級的延遲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.93,0:09:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為損害聯結的誘因也足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我們是怎樣聯結的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.82,0:09:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時空移動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.24,0:09:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然知道思考的傳達會產生1納秒的延遲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將思考傳送至1納秒未來 問題就解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.25,0:09:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事有可能嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.37,0:10:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本粒子等級的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.25,0:10:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本粒子等級？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.84,0:10:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼好笑的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.34,0:10:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果 博士還是不相信你的話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.80,0:10:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.14,0:10:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人看上去關係不錯 很好很好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.77,0:10:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在新型機上面搭載聯結系統？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.11,0:10:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒聽說嗎 很快就要讀出了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.24,0:10:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還只有兩台機體
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.11,0:10:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人物們古板的腦袋 也有點鬆緩了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 聯結機的量產也近在眼前了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾 還沒到這地步
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.21,0:10:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為聯合沒有重視聯結系統
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.46,0:10:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是被敵人緊逼不放呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為佐基利亞有那個人在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.97,0:10:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.93,0:10:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一樣 老師研究室的一個研究員
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.97,0:10:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃亡去了佐基利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.89,0:11:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是個優秀的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.35,0:11:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定深知艾維拉君的座艙的重要性
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.27,0:11:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人叫什麼名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.23,0:11:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(0,100)\pos(666,484)}佐基利亞科學院第2實驗研究所所長比盧海魯姆·哈恩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.40,0:11:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈恩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.61,0:11:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪盧海魯姆·哈恩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.95,0:11:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這是一個非常有趣的作戰哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.41,0:11:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我去和行政所說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝 哈恩博士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.75,0:11:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請加油 瑪格麗塔特務武官
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.04,0:11:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你來說 這可能是最後的機會了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願你奮戰到底
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.80,0:11:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slave 佐基利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.93,0:11:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上就是本次作戰的概要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.10,0:11:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中佐 哈恩博士到底是什麼人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.94,0:11:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區一介科學家 竟然能在行政局跟前說上話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.65,0:11:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是普通人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.07,0:11:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是你們應該知道的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.12,0:12:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我將親自上陣指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.17,0:12:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎 中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.09,0:12:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我啊 渡瀨青葉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.35,0:12:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就拉你上岸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.26,0:12:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我想讓你拿著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.56,0:12:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡瀨青葉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.48,0:12:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.52,0:12:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野牛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.02,0:12:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 一臉複雜的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.82,0:12:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛 你是怎麼從那座小島發出信號的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.11,0:12:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從接到信號 到我們抵達
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.08,0:12:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該沒有花費很久的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 FORTUNA的座艙已經沉入大海
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.54,0:12:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是從聯合的新型機那裡發出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.21,0:12:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 那你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.96,0:12:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 我在森林裡找到它
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:12:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正想要奪取的時候敵人卻回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.01,0:13:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只發出了求救信號
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.01,0:13:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我身上沒有武器…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那座島上 沒有FORTUNA以外的valiancer哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你們到達之前消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.02,0:13:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我藏起來了 所以沒怎麼看到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.53,0:13:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般來說 難以置信的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.99,0:13:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太碰巧了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.37,0:13:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這事跟中佐說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.20,0:13:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.37,0:13:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要告訴中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.25,0:13:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被特務武官閣下先察覺就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.29,0:13:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.63,0:13:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次要早點告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.71,0:13:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管發生什麼都會相信你的只有我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.42,0:13:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.89,0:13:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野牛 沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.01,0:13:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓緊時間搭乘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.64,0:13:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.28,0:14:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵方valiancer正在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.95,0:14:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至接觸為止還有10分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.49,0:14:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全體 對空戰鬥準備
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來 要出擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.13,0:14:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎 把那種狀態的兩個人放出來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.39,0:14:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 從一開始不就一直是那個樣子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.76,0:14:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.14,0:14:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散開準備戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.69,0:14:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不要想多餘的事 集中精神戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.07,0:14:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事我當然明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.99,0:14:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青葉同學 迪奧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請開始聯結
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.36,0:14:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.16,0:14:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.37,0:14:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連接迪奧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.74,0:14:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.71,0:14:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多數高熱源物體接近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.71,0:14:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是佐基利亞的巡航導彈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.96,0:14:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,nectar屏障展開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.84,0:15:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,損害如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.76,0:15:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部輕微受損 沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.39,0:15:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二波來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.77,0:15:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cygnus的nectar屏障的填充來不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.81,0:15:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各機 盡可能打落導彈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.23,0:15:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間驚訝了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.08,0:15:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著吧雛 這傢伙由我來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.63,0:15:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青葉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.50,0:15:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中佐掩護
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.75,0:15:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.34,0:15:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是那傢伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.05,0:15:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是纏人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.56,0:15:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.19,0:15:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿過去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.98,0:16:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Crane中彈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.11,0:16:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,康拉德大尉 將飛向Crane的導彈全部打落
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.57,0:16:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不允許繼續中彈了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.41,0:16:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.91,0:16:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事 Crane不會因為這種程度就沉的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.29,0:16:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾維拉君 我已經把你爺爺教我的東西全部告訴你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.25,0:16:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該到你畢業的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.34,0:16:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來就托付給你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.97,0:16:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼多怎麼打得完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.06,0:16:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說喪氣話 做該做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.19,0:16:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是青葉同學和迪奧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.73,0:16:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 只要等敵人打完導彈…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能打完就好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.53,0:16:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,導彈還在繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.24,0:16:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們到底是準備了多少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.41,0:16:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.33,0:16:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的目標是聯結時間終了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.50,0:17:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據哈恩博士的預測
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.79,0:17:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個新型機的聯結持續時間是300秒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.30,0:17:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 還有90秒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.43,0:17:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是解除聯結 這數量可不是鬧著玩的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.93,0:17:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手別停
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.35,0:17:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,導彈還在繼續飛過來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.06,0:17:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 聯結已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.06,0:17:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別放棄 渡瀨青葉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.11,0:17:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是決定留在Cygnus上戰鬥了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.36,0:17:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是個笨蛋 而且無可救藥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.28,0:17:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 自己決定的路無論發生什麼都要繼續前進
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是這種人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.66,0:17:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在Cygnus需要力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你 擁有回應這種需要的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.29,0:17:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥吧 為了需要你的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.63,0:17:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 你這愛哭鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.47,0:17:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 穿過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.93,0:17:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說我沒有了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.35,0:17:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.31,0:18:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少自以為是教育別人了 你這個妹控
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.06,0:18:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼 明明失落到不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.78,0:18:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在模仿你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.78,0:18:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙 哪壺不開提哪壺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.45,0:18:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個人一邊吵架…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.66,0:18:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊打落了那麼多的導彈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.16,0:18:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 時間已經不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.92,0:18:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距解除聯結還有10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.08,0:18:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.04,0:18:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.00,0:18:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.13,0:18:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.13,0:18:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.13,0:18:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.09,0:18:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.05,0:18:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.09,0:18:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.93,0:18:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.02,0:18:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒結束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.31,0:18:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯結被維持了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.90,0:18:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.28,0:18:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特務武官閣下 請指示
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.66,0:18:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續發射導彈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.53,0:18:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有誤差而已 聯結不可能持續很久
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.08,0:19:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射發射發射
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.71,0:19:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.96,0:19:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.96,0:19:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯結持續時間已經超過400秒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.34,0:19:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.47,0:19:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,導彈全部被迎擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.19,0:19:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.37,0:19:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脫…脫離
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.16,0:19:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開 打開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.63,0:19:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是應該死在這裡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.34,0:19:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.72,0:19:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您沒事吧 特務武官閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.26,0:19:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個聲音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:19:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾弗里德·加蘭特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.18,0:20:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰以失敗告終
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全機回艦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.48,0:20:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.95,0:20:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 愛哭鬼 你還挺能幹的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.91,0:20:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少囉嗦 妹控
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.66,0:20:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的聯結持續時間是429秒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.96,0:20:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以置信 竟然遠遠超過了理想值
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.46,0:20:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾維拉君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.67,0:20:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.63,0:20:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是優秀的聯結哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.05,0:20:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.30,0:20:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.64,0:20:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.25,0:21:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾 行政局似乎決定了你的調動
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.38,0:21:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近期就會有聯絡的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.84,0:21:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前好好休息一下如何
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.26,0:21:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是讓人羨慕啊 我有多少年沒有拿到休假了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.43,0:21:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈恩博士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.35,0:21:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事 阿爾弗里德中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.73,0:21:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天鵝既然進入了夏威夷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.69,0:21:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就無法再使用正攻法了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.94,0:21:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想實施之前呈報的作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.82,0:21:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呈報？什麼時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.28,0:21:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經跟上面說了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.70,0:21:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以和那個部隊立刻會合
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.79,0:21:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很期待你哦 阿爾弗里德中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.00,0:21:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slave 佐基利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.55,0:22:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時期派增援
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.72,0:22:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼樣的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.22,0:22:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔基姆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.14,0:22:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來了啊 里亞贊少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.19,0:22:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好嗎 雛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.48,0:22:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.94,0:23:41.82,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(650,479)}下回「父與子」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.27,0:23:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 BUDDY COMPLEX 父與子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.26,0:22:25.23,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心で呼ぶ　惹かれあう彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.26,0:22:25.23,EDZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心的呼應 響應的彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.33,0:22:33.88,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛みの理由(わけ)も忘れて　今だけどうか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.33,0:22:33.88,EDZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛的理由 請暫且忘記 我在此深深祈求
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.24,0:22:43.08,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,キミを知っている　キミを探しているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.24,0:22:43.08,EDZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我深知你 我在一直尋找著你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.12,0:22:51.80,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引き止められない光の残像に　そっとくちづけて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.12,0:22:51.80,EDZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕輕吻向那已飄渺的光的殘像
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.96,0:23:00.81,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躊躇いが僅かな　希望への糸口なら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.96,0:23:00.81,EDZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那稍稍的猶豫不決 成為了那連接希望的蛛絲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.84,0:23:09.52,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷徨った数だけ　優しい朝へ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.84,0:23:09.52,EDZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那微微的彷徨 拉近了與那溫柔黎明的距離
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.82,0:23:18.56,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あの空に還る未来で　救いたい　守りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.82,0:23:18.56,EDZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去拯救 想去保護 那早已歸還於天空的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.57,0:23:25.44,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その夢に届く未来で　待っていて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.57,0:23:25.44,EDZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請留步 那已經早已傳達過夢想的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.63,0:23:34.86,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きっと出会える愛に　手を伸ばして欲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.63,0:23:34.86,EDZ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能與我一起去抓住 那注定相遇的愛